description.en:
This set will attempt to quantify bullish or bearish conditions to add or subtract from the starting position. This set is based on an assessment of on-chain activity, token age spent, and technical analysis.

All trading decisions for this set will be made using the daily price chart on BraveNewCoin's ELX Index.

For the latest price analysis please see our insights page.
